---
title: Crispy Chicken Katsu with Honey-Sesame Carrots and Lemon Mayo
description: This delicious Japanese number is bound to be a crowd-pleaser. Crispy chicken katsu is perfectly paired with Honey-Sesame Carrots. Drizzle with a lemon-infused mayonnaise for a citrusy finish!
